text: Victor Matine is a Mozambican teacher and football coach who became manager of the Mozambique national football team in July 2019. He has previously coached the under-20 and under-23 national teams, as well as club side CD UP Manica. ==References== Category:Date of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Mozambican football managers Category:Mozambique national football team managers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
